OL,5, A French tourist has been jailed for   
OL,6, eight years for spying by a court in   
OL,7, Iran, his lawyer in Paris has said.    
OL,9,FBenjamin Briere, 36, was arrested in   
OL,10,FMay 2020 after flying a drone near the 
OL,11,FIran-Turkmenistan border.              
OL,13,FThe lawyer, Philippe Valent, said his  
OL,14,Fclient "did not have a fair trial in   
OL,15,Ffront of impartial judges", AFP news   
OL,16,Fagency reported.                       
OL,18,FHe said Mr Briere was "more and more   
OL,19,Fweak" from a hunger strike which he    
OL,20,Fbegan in December.                     
